description: Stand tall with elbows close to your sides and shoulders relaxed. Curl the weight upward by bending your elbows while keeping upper arms still. Lower slowly until your arms are fully extended. Maintain a neutral spine, steady breathing, and controlled movement throughout.

name: Lying Cable Curl
description: Stand tall with elbows close to your sides and shoulders relaxed. Curl the weight upward by bending your elbows while keeping upper arms still. Lower slowly until your arms are fully extended. Maintain a neutral spine, steady breathing, and controlled movement throughout.
